sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as CLI
  participant O as Orchestrator
  participant C as ChromaDB
  participant L as Azure LLM

  U->>O: uv run run_full.py
  opt arXiv augmentation
    O->>C: ingest papers - embed + add chunks
  end
  O->>L: trends.run - drivers from KB coverage gaps
  O->>L: merge.run - consolidate BOM + trend drivers
  O->>O: select_top_drivers - evidence-weighted, N=14
  O->>L: manifestations - 4 states x 14 = 56
  O->>L: cib.run - 5 personas x 2 Delphi rounds, 182 pairs
  O->>O: run_consistency - fixed points
  O->>L: scenario_gen.run
  O->>O: landscape.run - UMAP
  O->>L: evaluation.run - auditor then AHP + TOPSIS
  O->>O: temporal.run DVI + strategic_framing.run
  Note over O: fork - reuse morphbox + cib
  O->>O: run_combinatorial.run - soft-CIB, 120 scenarios
  O->>L: short narratives for kept combos
  O->>O: archetypes.run HDBSCAN+ordinal + structure.analyze_multi
  O-->>U: JSON artifacts in data/outputs/
